                                Quick Reference

     Unzip the files into your Wolfenstein directory (no files are
overwritten).  Enter VSWAP to alternate between the new graphics and the old.
Enter MAPS to alternate the new maps with the old ones.  Enter IDENTIFY to
find out what maps and graphics the game's set up to play.  These files are
for the 60-level version of Wolfenstein ONLY.
