                                 Installation

     Thank you for downloading my files!  The archive should contain the
following files:

W3D-OKBJ.DOC - This documentation.  Duh!
VSWAP.NEW    - The new graphics.
MAPHEAD.NEW  - The first part of the new levels.
GAMEMAPS.NEW - The second part of the new levels.
IDENTIFY.COM - An executable file
MAPS.COM     - Another executable file.
VSWAP.COM    - Yet another executable file.
SAVEGAM0.NEW - The first pre-saved game.
SAVEGAM1.NEW - The second pre-saved game.
